# 🍽️ Restaurant POS — Sơ đồ kết nối toàn bộ dự án

## Luồng chính (User Flow)

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["🏠 index.jsp"] --> B["🔑 /auth/login"]
    B --> C["🪑 /tables"]
    C -->|"Mở bàn"| D["📋 /menu?orderId=X"]
    D -->|"Thêm món"| D
    D -->|"Xác nhận đơn"| D
    D -->|"Hủy đơn"| C
    D -->|"Thanh toán"| E["💳 /checkout?orderId=X"]
    E -->|"Tiền mặt"| F["🧾 /checkout?view=receipt"]
    E -->|"VNPay"| G["🏦 /vnpay-pay"]
    G -->|"Callback"| H["🔄 /vnpay-return"]
    H -->|"Thành công"| F
    H -->|"Thất bại"| I["❌ vnpay-result.jsp"]
    C --> J["📋 /orders"]
    J -->|"Xem đơn OPEN"| D
    J -->|"Xem hoá đơn PAID"| F
    C --> K["📦 /admin/product"]
```

## Kết nối Controller → Service → DAO → Entity

| Controller | URL | Service | DAO | Entity | JSP View |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **AuthServlet** | `/auth/login`, `/register`, `/logout` | AuthenticationService | UserDAO, RoleDAO | User, Role | login.jsp, register.jsp |
| **TableServlet** | `/tables` | POSService → OrderService | TableDAO, AreaDAO, OrderDAO | RestaurantTable, Area, Order | tables.jsp |
| **MenuServlet** | `/menu` | POSService | OrderDAO, OrderDetailDAO, ProductDAO, CategoryDAO | Order, OrderDetail, Product, Category | menu.jsp |
| **CheckoutServlet** | `/checkout` | PaymentService, POSService | PaymentDAO, OrderDAO, TableDAO | Payment, Order | checkout.jsp, receipt.jsp |
| **VNPayServlet** | `/vnpay-pay`, `/vnpay-return` | PaymentService | PaymentDAO, OrderDAO, TableDAO | Payment, Order | vnpay-result.jsp |
| **ProductServlet** | `/admin/product` | POSService | ProductDAO, CategoryDAO | Product, Category | adminMenu.jsp, editProduct.jsp |
| **OrderServlet** | `/orders` | POSService | OrderDAO | Order | cart.jsp |

